<title>PRINCE OF PEACE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungtup Vawnchawih Minlun pen chuh,
 Tuhin ahung piengta'i;
 Sietlei, thangvan ah lal ta'n tin,
 Namtin in ho ta'n au.

[V2]
 2. A min - Mimak, Chamna Siempa,
 Kichamna Lal, Pathien;
 Kumsawt Pa, Lal lien hung hi'n tin,
 Kumsawt in pakcha'n au.

[V3]
 3. A thilbawl theihna pung intin,
 Minthang deuhdeuh in a;
 A vaihawmna hai ta puo'n tin,
 Lei kichamna'n dim hen.</lyrics>
</song>